# 0a686674fd4e4e5bae208c08f19a5694
#: ../../admin-guide/plugins/tcpinfo.en.rst:23
msgid ""
"This global plugin logs TCP metrics at various points in the HTTP "
"processing pipeline. The TCP information is retrieved by the "
":manpage:`getsockopt(2)` function using the ``TCP_INFO`` option. This is "
"only supported on systems that support the ``TCP_INFO`` option, currently"
" Linux and BSD."
msgstr ""

